{"tid":2255551,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我推咗個溝我個條女，但亦都同女朋友分咗手了","createTime":"2020-10-23T15:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T16:38:07.000Z","uid":15636,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fb09f3c79d2bb6e6f5410a6af73a7b342dc91d1d","tid":2255551,"uid":15636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"承接返上個PO<br />\n「點解要溝我，我唔想出軌呀」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2245201/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2245201/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝各位百屌成材，我知道自己其實未玩夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前覺得自己係個死毒撚，溝都女都算執到，一定要好好對人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知一有女埋身就心痕多出軌，個刻我都知自己仆街了<br />\n根本自己就係條人渣仆街，得一想二。<br />\n<br />\n分咗手呢一星期已經玩交友app食咗兩條女<br />\n原來溝女係咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無咗女朋友的確好空虛<br />\n我諗要過多一段時間先會習慣<br />\n<br />\n唔講了，岩岩完第1Q有感打既，浸埋浴出去第2Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52771393afbb39361b41f098fce499bf27308f1","tid":2255551,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"冇人想知"},{"pid":"7434828b9740d6984ab7c379ce7619ee707c6b71","tid":2255551,"uid":314731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"咁易食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4bd73956fa5e65f12452f68ba6a9486d8a0e3c","tid":2255551,"uid":15636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e52771393afbb39361b41f098fce499bf27308f1","tid":2255551,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"冇人想知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim